program shall enter into a formal agreement with the Secretary of the department
in which the Coast Guard is operating that provides that, upon the successful com-
pletion of a sea duty tour by such member, the Secretary of the department in
which the Coast Guard is operating shall, for a period equal to the length of the
sea duty tour, beginning on the date on which the sea duty tour concludes—
