as described in sections 920b, 920c(a), and 930 of title 10 (articles 120b, 120c,
and 130 of the Uniform Code of Military Justice); and
‘‘(7) domestic violence, as described in section 928b of title 10 (article 128b
of the Uniform Code of Military Justice).’’.
