the next in the chain of command, as appropriate, except in a case in which
the Inspector General determines that such notification would risk impair-
ing an ongoing investigation, would unnecessarily compromise the anonym-
ity of the individual making the allegation, or would otherwise be inappro-
priate; and
‘‘(2) to the extent practicable, shall be consistent with Department of Defense
