This section requires that the Commandant enter into memo-
randum of agreement with the Under Secretary of Commerce for
Oceans and Atmosphere to govern the use of the Storis to conduct
research or other scientific activities. The Commandant may also
enter into agreements with other Federal, state, local entities, in-
stitutions of higher education, or research institutes to use the
Storis to conduct research, facilitate science activities, data collec-
tion. The Commandant is prohibited from charging a fee for the
use of the Storis.
