Section 243. Direct hire authority for certain personnel
This section allows the Coast Guard to hire personnel in certain
positions directly.
Section 244. Command sponsorship for dependents of members of
Coast Guard assigned to Unalaska, Alaska
This section requires the Commandant to grant command spon-
