This section consolidates authorization for the Coast Guard Col-
lege Student Precommissioning Initiative and eliminates any ambi-
guity between competing statutory authorities regarding the Coast
Guard College Student Precommissioning Initiative that presently
exist in sections 2131 and 3710 of title 14, United States Code.
