locations in which there is a misalignment between the basic allow-
ance for housing rate and the prevailing housing coast for members
of the Coast Guard.
Section 606. Comptroller General report on safety and security in-
frastructure at Coast Guard Academy
This section requires the Comptroller General to study and re-
port on the safety and infrastructure at the Coast Guard Academy.
Section 607. Comptroller General study and report on permanent
