ess and military rotations of the Coast Guard. This report will de-
scribe current policies and costs, an evaluation of the effectiveness
of using contracted movers for changing stations, and assessments
of how the Coast Guard is meeting rotational goals. The report will
also generate recommendations for improving the permanent
change of station process for Coast Guard.
