§2103. Number and distribution of commissioned officers on
active duty promotion list
(a) MAXIMUM TOTAL NUMBER.—
(1) IN GENERAL.—The total number of Coast Guard commis-
sioned officers on the active duty promotion list, excluding war-
rant officers, shall not exceed—
