ceedings, afforded the right to obtain copies of records and doc-
uments relevant to the proceedings, and the right to appear be-
fore the board in person or by counsel or an accredited rep-
resentative of an organization recognized by the Secretary of
Veterans Affairs under chapter 59 of title 38.
