§3736. Precedence
(a) Reserve officers rank and take precedence in their respective
grades among themselves and with officers of the same grade on
the active duty [promotion list and the] promotion list, officers des-
ignated by the Secretary pursuant to this section, and the officers
on the permanent commissioned teaching staff in accordance with
